== Deploying to Heroku

Deploy [Integrity](http://integrityapp.com) on [Heroku](http://heroku.com)'s platform. Email and Campfire notification gems are enabled by default.

=== Installation

Get the repo;

    git clone git://github.com/sr/integrity-heroku
    cd integrity-heroku
    heroku create

Manually edit your Heroku URL and Github Token settings in init.rb

    c.base_url  "http://myapp.heroku.com"
    c.github    "TOKEN"

Commit and push;

    git commit -a -m "updated our heroku configuration"
    git push heroku master
    heroku rake db
    heroku open
